Package: parallelTools
Type: Package
Title: parallelTools
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-11-15
Author: Sebastian Warnholz
Maintainer: Sebastian Warnholz <sebastian.warnholz@fu-berlin.de>
Description: The package enables multicore functionality in Windows and other platforms without the need to rewrite the code when developing for different platforms. This is achieved by masking the function mclapply from the package parallel and using either clusterApply in Windoes or mclapply otherwise.
License: GPL-3
Depends: parallel
URL: https://github.com/wahani/parallelTools